data.description: Wow! You’ve got to see this home.  Nestled on one acre this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home transcends the ordinary.  Step inside to discover a dedicated office space, perfect for those seeking tranquility when working remotely. The elegant formal dining room sets the stage for unforgettable gatherings with hand-cut brick floors and custom woodwork. Calling All Cooks to the chef's kitchen with a gas stove and the perfect triangle design. In the Primary Suite, you'll find a spa-like bath complete with jetted tub and custom closet you won't want to go without. Between the secondary bedrooms, you'll find a unique media room perfect for making a podcast or musical jam session. From the covered back patio, enjoy morning coffee and space to entertain family and friends. Bonus Features: Custom Wine Closet, Half Bath in Garage, RV Electrical Hookup, Extra Wide Driveway, Backyard storage building. No detail has been overlooked in creating this extraordinary residence. No HOA, No MUD, No City Tax.
